			<iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/CbWqrL4pJeM?rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;wmode=transparent" width="400" height="300" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen title="JoomlaWorks AllVideos Player"></iframe>					</div>
